data.description: This beautiful home, located on a corner lot, is ready for it's next family. Brand new flooring throughout the entire downstairs. Plenty of yard space and NO HOA, so you have the freedom to create what you want. Hardwood floors throughout the upstairs of the home and plenty of rustic charm. Main Bedroom on the main floor with Large walk in closet that can also be used as an office. 3 large bedrooms upstairs with plenty of space. All brick exterior with a large eat-in kitchen, with main bedroom, laundry room and bathroom all on the first floor. Lots of natural light throughout the home as well
